 If we do the same algebraic calculations, 

00:02:35.058 --> 00:02:36.296
 we will have 

00:02:36.296 --> 00:02:41.156
 minus 7u is equal to minus 14x plus 2, 

00:02:41.809 --> 00:02:45.028
 or y is equal, just divide everything down to minus 7, 

00:02:45.028 --> 00:02:49.423
 2x minus 2/7. 

