 That does not look right, but you get a clue. 

00:03:27.744 --> 00:03:29.509
 These two do 

00:03:29.509 --> 00:03:30.507
 are parallel, 

00:03:30.507 --> 00:03:33.386
 therefore, no coordinate that satisfies these rights, 

00:03:33.386 --> 00:03:34.942
 will not satisfy this. 

00:03:34.942 --> 00:03:36.868
 They have no common points. 

00:03:36.868 --> 00:03:37.786
 They are parallel. 

00:03:37.786 --> 00:03:40.166
 This is the definition of parallelism. 

00:03:40.166 --> 00:03:43.567
 Because this and this rights have no common points, 

00:03:43.567 --> 00:03:45.448
 there is no way any of the solutions, 

00:03:45.448 --> 00:03:47.503
 which satisfies this equation, also satisfies this, 

00:03:47.503 --> 00:03:49.964
 because each (x, y) that satisfies this, 

00:03:49.964 --> 00:03:52.448
 will not satisfy this and vice versa. 

00:03:52.448 --> 00:03:53.249
 They are parallel. 

00:03:53.249 --> 00:03:54.364
 They have no common points. 

00:03:54.364 --> 00:03:56.824
 These two things will never cross. 

00:03:56.824 --> 00:04:00.006
 So Scarlett's system is not equivalent to that of the teacher. 

00:04:00.006 --> 00:04:02.502
 But what about Hanks? 

00:04:02.502 --> 00:04:04.104
 We see here that Hanks is here 

00:04:04.104 --> 00:04:05.346
 the same thing. 

00:04:05.346 --> 00:04:09.688
 5x minus y, but then the permanent member 

00:04:09.688 --> 00:04:13.101
