00:04:13.101 --> 00:04:16.502
 So this and this also represent parallel rows. 

00:04:16.502 --> 00:04:19.091
 Each pair (x, y) that satisfies this, 

00:04:19.091 --> 00:04:21.204
 will not satisfy that either. 

00:04:21.204 --> 00:04:23.003
 These two rules do not intersect. 

00:04:23.003 --> 00:04:24.489
 They are parallel. 

00:04:24.489 --> 00:04:28.651
 Hence, the Hanks system is also not equivalent to that of the teacher. 

